COPY ./scan_test.py .

VOLUME [ "/config" ]

ENV NGINX_WORKER_PROCESSES 1
ENV LISTEN_PORT 80

ENV TZ=Europe/London

ENTRYPOINT ["/app/entrypoint.sh"]
CMD ["/app/start.sh"]
